{"tid":1146131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女兒意外打碎花瓶「識破」13年暗儲私己錢 　丈夫無奈：好不容易藏點錢","createTime":"2019-05-09T05:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T18:16:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"62440a01e008cce4441cb0e0f21591c54c90eec0","tid":1146131,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T05:21:05.000Z","msg":"即使夫妻間可能都會暗藏「秘密」，廣西一名丈夫有儲「私己錢」習慣，並暗藏在花瓶13年，豈料花瓶日前意外被女兒「一掌打破」，讓他多年來的秘密曝光，相當無奈。<br />\n綜合內地傳媒報道，廣西桂林市的這名丈夫一直有省下伙食費，並把這筆「私己錢」儲起，藏在放置在家中客廳的一個大花瓶中，13年來從未被發現。<br />\n直到5月7日，女兒正在客廳中玩耍期間，妻子突然聽到巨響，<br />\n&quot;我（妻子）剛剛睜開眼睛坐在床上，突然客廳裡有個東西「啪啦」一聲響了。&quot;<br />\n嚇得她立刻跑到客廳察看，才發現原來是女兒不慎撞跌了花瓶，令花瓶當下碎裂。<br />\n不過令她更驚訝的是，<br />\n&quot;瓶子砸爛了怎麼那麼多錢？&quot;<br />\n當中包括1毫、2毫，甚至10元的人民幣紙鈔都有，於是她便給丈夫發訊息，要他回來一起研究這些「來歷不明」的錢。<br />\n丈夫得悉後馬上回來，甫進門卻已面露難色，<br />\n&quot;好不容易藏點錢，全被發現了。&quot;<br />\n無奈地「招認」這是自己從2006搬進這間屋後，儲下來13年的「私己錢」，讓妻子好氣又好笑。<br />\n經夫婦倆點算後，錢雖然儲了13年，但只有5000多元人民幣，讓妻子覺得「好搞笑」，而「被識破」的丈夫則表示「沒甚麼想法、沒甚麼心情」，並安慰自己<br />\n&quot;這個錢又不要緊。&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2345000/2346533/money_thumb_20190509_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2345000%2F2346533%2Fmoney_thumb_20190509_ch_1024.jpg&h=9337c480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2346533/%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E6%89%93%E7%A2%8E%E8%8A%B1%E7%93%B6%E3%80%8C%E8%AD%98%E7%A0%B4%E3%80%8D13%E5%B9%B4%E6%9A%97%E5%84%B2%E7%A7%81%E5%B7%B1%E9%8C%A2%20%E3%80%80%E4%B8%88%E5%A4%AB%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E8%97%8F%E9%BB%9E%E9%8C%A2?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2346533%2F%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%25A2%258E%25E8%258A%25B1%25E7%2593%25B6%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25AD%2598%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E3%2580%258D13%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%259A%2597%25E5%2584%25B2%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25B7%25B1%25E9%258C%25A2%2520%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%2588%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25A5%2588%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E6%2598%2593%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%25BB%259E%25E9%258C%25A2%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYdqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=110c849a\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2346533/%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E6%89%93%E7%A2%8E%E8%8A%B1%E7%93%B6%E3%80%8C%E8%AD%98%E7%A0%B4%E3%80%8D13%E5%B9%B4%E6%9A%97%E5%84%B2%E7%A7%81%E5%B7%B1%E9%8C%A2%20%E3%80%80%E4%B8%88%E5%A4%AB%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88%EF%BC%9A%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E8%97%8F%E9%BB%9E%E9%8C%A2?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"2159f42f4dcb9b9622cb5e653fa0781a07829939","tid":1146131,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:44:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e6c721e3928127e7520f1b7d1fbd70c7ee33041","tid":1146131,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:46:43.000Z","msg":"衰女包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d507939f3891488877c2955c00b648d8e2c201d","tid":1146131,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />據說，蓮燈仔成日話大陸妹好溫柔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e1a0e981343899d289976b63aeb265739b92cc","tid":1146131,"uid":136985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:47:54.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"2f932d31df50893ae2a5122ba41363a3c9411da5","tid":1146131,"uid":11148,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"但只有5000多元人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=